{"tid":368452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大學教授及立法者可提名黃之鋒成為諾貝爾和平獎候選人","createTime":"2017-08-21T14:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T07:34:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a430e16be02988a3364f940684fa7761cfb3154","tid":368452,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:21:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170821/20127955\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170821%2F20127955&d=T5GqAMoknpQKFzmuFUSIuzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=2f435934\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170821%2F20127955&h=44bdee9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170821/20127955</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20141008/640_fb3f3308dcf692978a9400cc2bf806dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20141008%2F640_fb3f3308dcf692978a9400cc2bf806dd.jpg&h=6c4e36c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】黃之鋒等人有機會成為諾貝爾和平獎的參選人，過往亦有不少華人獲得提名。除了2010年的已故諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波外，流亡海外民運人士魏京生最少六度獲提名。<br />\n<br />\n若想競逐諾貝爾和平獎，只需任何一位有資格者支持便可提名，合資格者如大學教授、立法者、諾貝爾獎獲獎人和委員會成員。<br />\n<br />\n和平獎的委員會不公開入圍名單，但過往提名人都會公開表示提名了何人，故外界得知該年有誰參選。"},{"pid":"142e80ab9b8f51d63752d33ea454d48eac48a743","tid":368452,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"[URL=<a href=\"http://makeagif.com/gif/so-sorry-jinping-ko-gussa-kyu-aata-hai-dN-M_0]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmakeagif.com%2Fgif%2Fso-sorry-jinping-ko-gussa-kyu-aata-hai-dN-M_0%5D&d=T5GqAMoknpQKFzmuFUSIuzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=fb726c2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://makeagif.com/gif/so-sorry-jinping-ko-gussa-kyu-aata-hai-dN-M_0]</a><img src=\"http://i.makeagif.com/media/8-21-2017/dN-M_0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F8-21-2017%2FdN-M_0.gif&h=427fde25&s={SIZE}\" />[/URL]"},{"pid":"ac2296a346fe1fa7d2dfc4e199df292939b92523","tid":368452,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒會否成為坐最短監既諾貝爾和平獎候選人?"},{"pid":"cc59cd9d0ffa935b0c326853595be5e0be4a7f6d","tid":368452,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:34:54.000Z","msg":"和平獎參選人<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母死蘋果，而家係咪唔識字都可以寫文稿 ?"}]}